quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Achiika! Ninvuɣu shεba ban ti Naawuni yεlimaŋli nya tarli
  23,2,Bana n-nyɛ ninvuɣu shεba ban filindi bɛ maŋ’ (n-tiri Naawuni) bɛ jiŋli ni
  23,3,Ni ninvuɣu shεba ban lebri biriti ka chɛ yεltɔɣakaha
  23,4,Ni ninvuɣu shεba ban tiri zaka
  23,5,Ni ninvuɣu shεba ban guri bɛ tooni (ka chɛ zina niŋbu)
  23,6,"Naɣila ni bɛ paɣaba, bee bɛ sulinsi, tɔ! Achiika! Bannim’ maa pala bɛ ni galindi shεba"
  23,7,"Dinzuɣu, ŋun ti bo din pa dimbɔŋɔ- nim’ maa nyaaŋa, tɔ! Bannim’ maa nyɛla ninvuɣu shεba ban kpahi yεɣi"
  23,8,Ni ninvuɣu shεba ban guri bɛ daamaananim’ mini bɛ daalikauli
  23,9,Ni ninvuɣu shεba ban guri bɛ jiŋli
  23,10,Bannim’ maa n-nyɛ falidiriba
  23,11,"Bana n-nyɛ ninvuɣu shεba ban yɛn ti di Firdausi Daalizanda fali, ka bɛ nyɛla ban yɛn ti kpalim di puuni"
  23,12,Yaha! Achiika! Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) namla ninsala (Annabi Adam) ka o pilli nyɛ yεɣiri
  23,13,"Din nyaaŋa ka Ti zali o (Adam bia) ka o nyɛla maniyyi (dablim kom), ka di be bɛhigu shee din nyɛ suhudoo shee"
  23,14,"Din nyaaŋa, ka Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) zaŋ dablim kom maa n-nam ʒitalli, ka zaŋ ʒitalli maa n-nam nimkpilli, ka zaŋ nimkpilli maa n-nam din nyaaŋa ka Ti nam o ka o nyɛla koba, ka zaŋ mimdi n-limsi koba maa, binnamdi shɛli. Dinzuɣu, Naawuni so Ŋun mi nambu n-gari sokam maa nam tibgiya"
  23,15,"Di nyaaŋa, achiika! Yi nyɛla ban yɛn kpi"
  23,16,"Din nyaaŋa, achiika! Yi nyɛla bɛ ni yɛn ti yiɣisi shεba Zaadali"
  23,17,Yaha! Achiika! Ti namla sagbana ayɔpoin yi zuɣusaa. Ti mi pala ban tamdi binnamda yεla